<del rend="strikethrough">dıe von </del> der Rate cʒu
                                <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan> botſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r3l37">
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_42_r3l36">von Jm geuertıgt </ab></add> hat / daʒ wir
