<expan>paſc<ex>ae</ex></expan> / viij<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_42" id="19v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Weiszemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> weisheit
                        villeiht wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> hat von
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Toplers wegen, als den die von
                                <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> in ir venknüsse genomen
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wir nu
                                <expan>newlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> erber botschaft <add>czu in</add> gen
                                <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> getan
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <add>die</add> in etwaz
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<add>davon</add> erczelt hat; darauff der rate czu
                            <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan> botschaft <add>von im gevertigt</add> hat, daz
                        wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> botschaft in den oster feyertagen schierst
                        wol darümb czu in wider schicken mügen, darümb sie uns und auch
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> steten, die ir botschaft dohin tun
                        werden, ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>czugeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mainen; nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> wie daz gemain stete <add>des
                            punds</add> in <expan>Swab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>darumb</add> ir erber botschafft <add>gen</add>
<expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auf den <app><note><q type="date">afftermontag <add>czu naht</add>
                        in <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> osterveyertagen</q>17.04.1408</note></app>
<expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> wollen. So <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir auch <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, etlich
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> rats <pb facs="#facs_43" id="20r"/>und erber
                        botschaft auf <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag gen
                                <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> darümb czeschicken; davon geviel
                        ez <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit, <add>so geviel uns wol</add>, daz
                        ir <add>auch czwen</add> ewrs rats gen Rotemburg auf den
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> tag von
                                <add><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> stat
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></add> geschickt het, <add>daz die czu
                            abent da <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan></add>,
                            <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir mainen, daz das in den
                                <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vast
                            <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und gut wer.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vig<ex>i</ex>lia</expan>
<expan>pasc<ex>ae</ex></expan> viii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
